text: Marian Więckowski (8 September 1933 - 17 July 2020) was a Polish racing cyclist.Nie żyje Marian Więckowski He won the Tour de Pologne in 1954, 1955 and 1956. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1933 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Polish male cyclists Category:Sportspeople from Warsaw
